1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,000
Enterprise teams are scaling GenAI, but direct model integrations create risk:
fragmented security, unpredictable cost, and vendor lock-in.

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:11,500
llm_gateway solves this with one control plane
in front of every LLM provider.

3
00:00:11,500 --> 00:00:18,500
With a single endpoint, teams get policy-based routing,
automatic failover, and scoped API key governance.

4
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:24,500
Plus Redis caching, live cost tracking,
and full audit visibility.

5
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:30,000
That means faster delivery, better reliability,
and measurable cost control across AI workloads.
